quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  19,59,Koma mibadwo ya anthu imene inadza iwo atachoka idanyoza mapemphero ndi kutsatira zilakolako zawo. Ndithudi awa adzakumana ndi mavuto
  19,60,Kupatula amene alapa machimo ndi kukhulupirira choonadi ndi kumachita ntchito zabwino. Iwo adzalowa ku Paradiso ndipo sadzaponderezedwa m’chilichonse
  19,61,"Iwo adzakhala m’minda ya Edeni mpaka muyaya, imene Mwini chisoni chosatha adalonjeza akapolo ake ngakhale kuti iwo sadaione. Ndithudi lonjezo lake lidzakwaniritsidwa"
  19,62,"Kumeneko iwo sadzamva zinthu zopanda pake koma mawu a mtendere okha, ndipo chakudya chidzapatsidwa kwa iwo m’mawa ndi madzulo"
  19,63,Imeneyo ndiyo Paradiso imene tidzawapatsa akapolo athu omwe anali kuopa Mulungu
  19,64,"Ife sititsika kuchoka kumwamba pokhapokha ngati taloledwa ndi Ambuye wako. Iye ndiye mwini wa zinthu zonse zimene zili pamaso pathu, kumbuyo kwathu ndi zonse zimene zili pakati pa zimenezi. Ndipo Ambuye wako saiwala"
  19,65,Ambuye wa kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili mmenemo. Kotero m’pembedze Iye yekha ndipo khala wopirira pamapemphero ake. Kodi ukudziwa wina amene ali ndi dzina ngati la Iye
  19,66,"Munthu amati, “Pamene ine nditafa kodi ndidzaukitsidwa ndi kukhalanso ndi moyo?”"
  19,67,Kodi munthu sakumbukira kuti tidamulenga iye pamene poyamba sadali chinthu china chilichonse
  19,68,Motero pali Ambuye wako; ndithudi Tidzawasonkhanitsa pamodzi ndi a Satana ndipo onse tidzawabweretsa m’mphepete mwa Gahena atagwada
  19,69,Ndipo mwachoonadi tidzachotsa mugulu lililonse onse amene adanyoza Mulungu kwambiri
  19,70,Ndithudi Ife tilikuwadziwa kwambiri amene ali oyenera kuotchedwa
  19,71,Palibe wina wa inu amene sadzapita kumbali ya Moto. Limeneli ndilo lamulo la mphamvu la Ambuye wanu
  19,72,"Ndipo Ife tidzapulumutsa onse amene amaopa ndi kuwasiya ochita zoipa, atagwada, kuti amve ululu wake"
  19,73,"Pamene zivumbulutso zathu zilakatulidwa momveka kwa iwo, anthu osakhulupirira amanena kwa anthu okhulupirira kuti, “Kodi ndi gulu liti pa magulu awiriwa limene lili ndi malo abwino okhala ndi anthu apamwamba?”"
  19,74,"Kodi ndi mibadwo ingati yakale imene tidaononga iwo asanadze, mibadwo imene idali ndi zinthu zabwino ndiponso zokongola"
  19,75,"Nena, “Aliyense amene alakwa, Mwini chisoni chosatha adzawaonjezera nthawi, mpaka pamene adzaone zomwe adalonjezedwa. Kaya ndi chilango kapena ola lomaliza, pamenepo ndiye adzadziwa kuti ndani amene ali mwini wa malo oipa ndi gulu lankhondo lofoka.”"
  19,76,Mulungu amapitiriza kutsogolera iwo amene atsatira njira yoyenera. Ntchito zabwino zimene zili ndi malipiro osatha zili ndi mphotho yabwino pamaso pa Ambuye wako ndiponso zotsatira zake ndi zabwino
  19,77,"Kodi mwamuona munthu amene akana zivumbulutso zathu ndipo amanena kuti, “Ine, ndithudi, ndidzapatsidwa chuma ndi ana?”"
  19,78,Kodi iye waziona zinthu zosaoneka kapena Mwini chisoni chosatha wamupatsa lonjezo lotere
  19,79,Osatheka! Ife tidzalemba zimene akunena ndi kuchipanga chilango chake kukhala chachitali
  19,80,Zonse zimene azilankhula iye zidzabwerera kwa Ife ndipo adzadza pamaso pathu yekha
  19,81,Anthu osakhulupirira adadzisankhira milungu ina kuti iwapatse mphamvu ndi ulemerero
  19,82,Ayi. Koma milunguyo idzakana kupembedza kwawo ndipo idzakhala adani awo
  19,83,Kodi siudaone kuti timatumiza kwa anthu osakhulupirira a Satana amene amawaonetsa zinthu zoti achimwe nazo
  19,84,"Kotero musafulumize kuwapemphera chionongeko, ndithudi, tikuwawerengera masiku awo"
  19,85,Tsiku limenetidzasonkhanitsaanthuolungamam’magulu kufika pamaso pa Ambuye wachisoni kudzalandira ulemu
  19,86,Ndipo tidzawakusa anthu oipa kupita ku moto wa ku Gahena ali ndi ludzu lodetsa nkhawa
  19,87,Palibe amene adzakhala ndi mphamvu zodandaula kupatula yekhayo amene walandira chilolezo cha Mwini chisoni chosatha
  19,88,"Iwo amati, “Mwini chisoni chosatha wabala mwana wamwamuna.”"
  19,89,Ndithudi mwanena chinthu choipitsitsa
  19,90,Pafupifupi kumwamba kumafuna kung’ambika chifukwa cha mawu amenewa ndipo nthaka imafuna kugawikana ndi mapiri kugudubuzika ndi kuonongeka
  19,91,Chifukwa chonena Mwini Chisoni Chosatha ali ndi mwana wamwamuna
  19,92,Si zoyenera kwa Mwini chisoni chosatha kuti akhale ndi mwana
  19,93,Palibe china chilichonse chimene chili kumwamba kapena pa dziko lapansi chimene chimabwera kwa Mwini chisoni chosatha kupatula ngati kapolo
  19,94,Iye wasunga chiwerengero cha zolengedwa zake zonse
  19,95,"Ndipo onse, mmodzimmodzi, adzabwerera kwa Iye pa tsiku la kuuka kwa akufa"
  19,96,"Ndithudi amene akhulupirira ndi kuchita ntchito zabwino, Mwini chisoni chosatha adzawakonda"
  19,97,Motero Ife tapanga iyo kukhala yosavuta ya m’chiyankhulo chako kuti upeleke nkhani yabwino kwa anthu oopa ndi kuchenjeza ndi ilo anthu otsutsa
  19,98,Kodi ndi mibadwo ingati imene Ife tidaononga kale iwo asanadze? Kodi uli kumuona mmodzi aliyense wa iwo kapena kumva manong’onong’o ochokera kwa iwo